title: Aurel Kolnai - The war against the west 1938
description:
Aurel Kolnai

The war against the west - 1938



Published in 1938, The War Against the West is a critical study of German National Socialism written by Aurel Kolnai. It describes German National Socialism as diametrically opposed to the [classical] liberal, democratic, Constitutional, and free-enterprise "Western" tendencies found mainly within Britain and the United States.
